🔤 Additional Character Checking Functions

isspace(ch)
✔ Checks for whitespace characters
(space ' ', tab \t, newline \n, vertical tab \v, form feed \f, carriage return \r)

isblank(ch)
✔ Checks for space or tab only

isprint(ch)
✔ Checks for printable characters (including space)

isgraph(ch)
✔ Checks for printable characters except space

iscntrl(ch)
✔ Checks for control characters (non-printable like \n, \t, etc.)

isxdigit(ch)
✔ Checks for hexadecimal digits
(0-9, a-f, A-F)

🔄 Character Conversion Functions

tolower(ch)
✔ Converts uppercase letter to lowercase

toupper(ch)
✔ Converts lowercase letter to uppercase
